{
  "stem": "23572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pesach was a tradition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to go over to my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His name was Abich Frenkel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a half brother to my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, my-- Gershon Ucker, I think my mother, [NON-ENGLISH] is probably part of even the second or the third marriage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But from the first marriage or second marriage, he had other sons and daughters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And two of them lived in Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one of them, it was tradition that we used to go to him for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the other guest at the house all the time was Dr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Joseph Borg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As I'm sure Israelis would know, he was the minister of Religious Affairs, and his son today is, I think, the head of the Jewish agency, or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Borg, I sat at the same table as Joseph Borg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was a kid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If I reminded him I was there, he wouldn't remember it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But if I mentioned my uncle's name, he certainly would know who I'm talking about, because they were very-- he was a professor at the [NON-ENGLISH] school gymnasium where I went to.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was very well known.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Joseph Borg was also at the holidays.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember Hanukkah, and Purim, and Rosh Hashanah, and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We'd all go to shul in those days, the men used to wear high-- high top hats and everything else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I surely remember the holidays, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who was doing the cooking?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, my mother did the cooking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the beginning, I remember I think 1931, I think we had the lady come into the house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if she did the cooking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had a live-in maid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to call her Fraulein, which is Miss.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
